sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as Platform Orchestrator<br/>(rhods-operator)
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Operator as workbenches-operator<br/>(controller-runtime)
    participant WBNamespace as Workbench Namespace<br/>(rhods-notebooks)
    participant Deployments as Workbench Deployments<br/>(label: app.opendatahub.io/workbenches=true)

    Note over Orchestrator,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Workbenches Reconciliation

    Orchestrator->>K8sAPI: CREATE/UPDATE Workbenches CR<br/>(gatewayDomain, platform, mlflowEnabled)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event: Workbenches CR changed

    Operator->>K8sAPI: GET Workbenches CR<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Workbenches spec<br/>(managementState, workbenchNamespace, etc.)

    alt managementState == "Managed"
        Note over Operator: configureDependencies()
        Operator->>K8sAPI: CREATE/UPDATE Namespace<br/>(rhods-notebooks or opendatahub)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Namespace created/updated
        K8sAPI-->>WBNamespace: Namespace exists with labels

        Note over Operator: checkDeployments()
        Operator->>K8sAPI: LIST Deployments in workbench namespace<br/>(label selector: app.opendatahub.io/workbenches=true)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>Operator: Deployment list with readiness status

        Note over Operator: computeKustomizeParams()<br/>(computed but not yet applied)

        Operator->>K8sAPI: UPDATE Workbenches CR status<br/>(Ready, ProvisioningSucceeded,<br/>Degraded, DeploymentsAvailable)<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    else managementState == "Removed"
        Note over Operator: Teardown flow (cleanup resources)
        Operator->>K8sAPI: UPDATE Workbenches CR status<br/>(conditions reflect removed state)
    end

    Note over Operator: Requeue after 30s for<br/>deployment health checks<br/>(exponential backoff: 5s base, 5m max on errors)

    Note over Orchestrator,Deployments: Metrics Collection (separate flow)
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus
    Prometheus->>Operator: GET /metrics<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (SubjectAccessReview)
    Operator-->>Prometheus: Metrics response
